linuxstudio (1.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Bug fixes and improvements
  * Fixed scene command implementation
  * Enhanced installation verification with version checks
  * Improved embedded system compatibility
  * Added force overwrite for binary updates
  * Better SSL certificate handling for embedded systems
  * Enhanced download progress display

